<div class="mw-parser-output"><h1>Broadcast (240)</h1>
<p>Usage:
</p>
<pre> broadcast &lt;string&gt;
</pre>
<p>Displays a string for all connected characters. Similar to the echo command, but with a reach that spans the entire game rather than just a specific room.
</p><p>See also:
</p>
<pre> &gt; <a cmd='#'>wizhelp echo</a>
 &gt; <a cmd='#'>wizhelp message</a>
</pre>




</div>